# Security response headers for both Cloudflare Pages projects
# (pencheff.com + app.pencheff.com). Cloudflare Pages serves these from
# out/_headers. x-content-type-options and referrer-policy are already
# set upstream, so only the missing four are added here.
#
# CSP is intentionally minimal: frame-ancestors (clickjacking) +
# upgrade-insecure-requests only. No script-src/default-src, so it cannot
# break the Clerk-auth Next.js app. Harden with a script policy later
# behind report-only testing.
/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Permissions-Policy: accelerometer=(), camera=(), geolocation=(), gyroscope=(), magnetometer=(), microphone=(), payment=(), usb=()
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self'; upgrade-insecure-requests
